    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pan with the <strong>chopped ginger </strong>and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
