    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>chickpeas</strong></p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>butternut squash cubes </strong>and<strong> drained chickpeas</strong> to the pan with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong> and cook, covered, for 15-20 min or until the squash is fork-tender – this is your <strong>curried squash & chickpeas</strong></p>",
