    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the squash is cooking, add your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> with your <strong>mango chutney</strong>, a splash of <strong>milk</strong> and season with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and blitz until smooth and creamy – this is your <strong>whipped Greek cheese</strong></p>",
